---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout
  title="Accessibility Statement - HeshbonAI"
  description="Accessibility statement for the HeshbonAI website, including our accessibility efforts, standards target, and contact details for reporting issues."
  canonical="https://heshbonai.co/accessibility"
>
  <Navbar />

  <main class="pt-24">
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-navy">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <p class="section-label mb-4 text-center">Accessibility</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white text-center">
          Accessibility Statement
        </h1>
        <p class="text-muted text-lg md:text-xl mt-6 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          HeshbonAI is committed to making this website accessible to as many people as possible,
          including people with disabilities.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-navy-light">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="card">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Our commitment</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              We work to improve the usability and accessibility of this website on an ongoing basis.
              Our goal is to support a practical accessibility baseline aligned with common WCAG Level AA
              expectations and the accessibility obligations typically applied to websites serving users in Israel.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Accessibility features on this site</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-muted leading-relaxed">
              <li>Keyboard-friendly navigation and visible focus indicators.</li>
              <li>A skip link that allows keyboard users to jump directly to the main content.</li>
              <li>Responsive layouts designed to work across desktop and mobile devices.</li>
              <li>Support for reduced-motion preferences where possible.</li>
              <li>Semantic headings, buttons, and navigation patterns across key pages.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Known limitations</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              We continue to review and improve the website. Some content, third-party integrations,
              or future updates may not yet provide the optimal accessibility experience in every case.
              If you encounter a specific issue, we want to hear about it so we can address it.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Need help or found an issue?</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
              If you experience an accessibility barrier while using this site, please contact us with:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-muted leading-relaxed mt-4">
              <li>The page or feature you were trying to use.</li>
              <li>A short description of the issue.</li>
              <li>The device, browser, or assistive technology you were using, if relevant.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mt-4">
              Contact: <a href="mailto:support@heshbonai.co" class="text-blue hover:text-blue-soft underline underline-offset-2">support@heshbonai.co</a>
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Statement updated</h2>
            <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Last updated: March 2026.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
